{\pntxtb (}{\pntxta )}}{\*\pnseclvl9\pnlcrm\pnstart1\pnindent720\pnhang{\pntxtb (}{\pntxta )}}\pard\plain \qj\ri51\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\lang1034\cgrid {\b\fs28 Sentencia C-636/96
